#: model:ir.model.fields,help:purchase_mrp.field_mrp_bom_line__cost_share
msgid ""
"The percentage of the component repartition cost when purchasing a kit.The "
"total of all components' cost have to be equal to 100."
msgstr ""
"ເປີເຊັນການແບ່ງປັນຕົ້ນທຶນສ່ວນປະກອບເມື່ອຊື້ຊຸດ (kit). ຕົ້ນທຶນທັງໝົດຂອງທຸກສ່ວນປະກອບຕ້ອງເທົ່າກັບ 100."

#. module: purchase_mrp
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/purchase_mrp/models/mrp_bom.py:0
#, python-format
msgid "The total cost share for a BoM's component have to be 100"
msgstr "ສ່ວນແບ່ງຕົ້ນທຶນທັງໝົດສຳລັບສ່ວນປະກອບຂອງ BOM ຕ້ອງເທົ່າກັບ 100"
